data.title: The Blues Highway Tue Mar 28 with Pat Graham on KLBP
data.meta_description:
Hi, I’m Pat Graham inviting you to join me Tuesday evenings at 5pm
 for “The Blues Highway” right here on 99.1 FM, KLBP. Together we’ll 
listen to masters from the past and today's living legends. It’s two hours of nonstop blues. So I’ll see you Tuesday evenings, right here on 99.1 FM,KLBP and KLBP.org for The Blues Highway.
